<br />I'm no expert of GB/GBC nor GBA, but an emulator is an emulator. Because a program works on it doean't mean it will work on a true Gameboy, and vice versa. I don't know about Gomba Color, but I'm pretty sure there is a lot if inaccuracies in Lameboy, the GB/GBC emulator for the DS (that I use a lot).

		

		</td>
